{
  "type": "doc",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "A cross-stitch alphabet sampler is the standard first finished piece in counted-thread embroidery. Each letter is made of small X-shaped stitches on a grid-woven cloth called Aida. The chart below shows where each X goes; you count squares from your starting point and work across.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "This sampler is a 26-letter alphabet border in three colours, 88 stitches wide and 28 stitches tall. about 16 by 5 cm of stitched area on 14-count Aida. The letter shapes are taken unchanged from the ",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "text": "samp-letter",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "glossaryTooltip",
              "attrs": {
                "termId": "cmpb7qm6j0000g4v4uaszzgp5"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " alphabets in Therese de Dillmont's Encyclopedia of Needlework (1886).",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "New to cross-stitch?",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "bold"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " Read ",
          "type": "text"
        },
        {
          "text": "How to cross-stitch",
          "type": "text",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "techniqueLink",
              "attrs": {
                "label": "How to cross-stitch",
                "techniqueSlug": "how-to-cross-stitch"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": " first. it covers holding the hoop, working a single X, and starting and ending a thread.",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "attrs": {
        "level": 2
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "What you need",
          "type": "text"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bulletList",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "14-count Aida cloth",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": ", a 30 by 13 cm piece in white or cream.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Stranded cotton in three colours",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": ", one skein each. The pattern uses DMC 815 (deep red), DMC 522 (sage), DMC 832 (muted gold). Any three contrasting shades work.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Size 24 tapestry needle",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": ". blunt-tipped, large eye.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "15 cm embroidery hoop",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "listItem",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": [
                {
                  "text": "Embroidery scissors",
                  "type": "text",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "bold"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
